	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=494><span id=Scholar>Braun</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>56 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.90]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Don't use 2H weapons to taunt.<br><br>I use the fastest 1H weapons I can get my grubby hands on.&nbsp;&nbsp;The key is to have more attacks on the hate list to move you up it. Also, when you hit taunt, you ALWAYS become the target on a successful taunt. If your using a slow 2H weapon, the first person who hits it after you taunt becomes enemy #1 on the list.  <br><br>I use a Jade mace in primary and Jarsath Trident in other with my Cloak of Flames.  I can effectivly taunt off a monk who is using a Tranq staff and can keep up with those deathwish rangers.</p>&nbsp;<br>Braun - 59ish Ogre Warrior<br>Torvonnilous</td></td></tr>
